      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PAYNE CARGO (2) was a last start winner (25.35) at Gunnedah in a Grade 5 and will jump from box 2 for the first time. Has never missed the frame at the trip from four starts. Ran one of the fastest times on the program in his latest win. In sparkling form and looks the one to beat again. BLUE CHANELLE (1) put in a much better performance last start when in the placings at The Gardens behind George Judy (23.11) in a Grade 3/4. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Some good form is emerging from her last run. Expected to feature again. ZIPPING DELORIS (5) goes very well this course and distance starting five times for two wins and two minors. Hit the frame latest (23.21) when third at The Gardens in a Grade 3/4. Looks well placed here and among the chances. MID CITY BOSS (8) drops in trip and is worth considering.",
